23
00:03:05,467 --> 00:03:06,716
Oh, there you are, Toni.

24
00:03:10,965 --> 00:03:11,942
Thank you.

25
00:03:12,702 --> 00:03:14,496
Some men are so stupid.

26
00:03:15,097 --> 00:03:18,317
Meaning anyone in particular?
- Meaning the Herr Direktor.

27
00:03:18,722 --> 00:03:20,394
Herr Direktor is a very brilliant man.

28
00:03:20,609 --> 00:03:22,189
Hmm. He's blind.

29
00:03:22,668 --> 00:03:24,649
Toni .. that's not very nice of you.

30
00:03:24,968 --> 00:03:26,921
Here he is, year after year.

31
00:03:27,240 --> 00:03:28,856
With his nose in the clouds.

32
00:03:29,241 --> 00:03:32,246
Running the school, teaching
history and writing books.

33
00:03:32,602 --> 00:03:34,953
