553
00:35:45,741 --> 00:35:48,511
Whatever it is, you mustn't
be afraid to tell me.

554
00:35:52,688 --> 00:35:55,364
It was wrong to write what I did, but ..

555
00:35:57,298 --> 00:35:58,763
