556
00:36:01,179 --> 00:36:03,020
But you're so young, Marie.

557
00:36:03,902 --> 00:36:04,682
Young.

558
00:36:08,596 --> 00:36:10,812
That letter was something
I wished were true.

559
00:36:12,127 --> 00:36:13,282
And in writing it.

560
00:36:14,118 --> 00:36:16,099
I seemed to make it <i>come</i> true.

561
00:36:18,503 --> 00:36:20,066
